column2: "We owe this victory to you three. Allow me to thank you once again."
"If anything it was all thanks to your song, Nadereh."
"Fair... But I never would have been able to use it if Manon had not been around."
"The threat of the DOLLS has still not been quashed completely..."
"But Retem City should be able to find some stability now."
"So it is our turn to help now. We will engage in formal cooperation with Central."
"Crawford and I have already spoken about it. I look forward to collaborating together."

"Oh, stop it. I'm not used to singing in front of a crowd."
msc_012300_0140#0,"But you're always so imposing."""
"Come again any time, you are always welcome."
"I'll perform for you whenever you like."
"Alright, let's head back to Central City!"
